# =============================================================================
#  MWA2 — source repo .gitignore
#  This repo tracks the SOURCE (our Python, mods, docs, catalogs). The RUNNABLE
#  PACKAGE (game worlds + bundled Python + PPeX) is assembled by copy, not git.
#  Our mod files inside the worlds are tracked EXPLICITLY via `git add -f`.
# =============================================================================

# --- Game worlds (tens of GB) — our mods inside are force-added ---------------
/school/
/jail/

# --- Bundled runtime + build outputs (large binaries; shipped, not committed) -
/system/python/
/system/ppex/
/system/mutexfind/

# --- Runtime state / saves / per-playthrough data ----------------------------
/_playthroughs/
/_backup/
*.flag
*.sav
*.json.tmp
_ppex_server.log

# --- Build artifacts ---------------------------------------------------------
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/Backup/

# --- Python ------------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# --- Editor / OS / tooling ---------------------------------------------------
.vs/
*.user
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.claude/
